messages.content:
Is it possible to do assertions on the lengths of Field arrays? Currently I have something like:

```
    if (A[0].length !== B.length) {
        throw new Error("Matrix dimensions do not match for multiplication.");
    }
```

But it would be better as an assertion, I assume it won't play nice with o1js if I'm throwing errors like this?

I am currently doing:

```
    Field(A[0].length).assertEquals(Field(B.length), "Matrix dimensions do not match for multiplication.");
```

But not sure if this is the best way - doesn't seem very idiomatic o1js. Any insight would be appreciated!
